error[expander::invalid-binding-name]: Invalid binding name
  ╭▸ 
5 │   ["+", { "#literal": 1 }, { "#literal": 2 }],
  │   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ expected a simple identifier for the `let` binding name
  │
  ├ help: write `(let name value body)` with a plain name such as `x`
  ╰ note: the first argument to `let` introduces a new local binding and must be a plain identifier without path qualification or generic arguments